## Changelog
* a002aa41c75d16dcdda2b5f45acce122e5ba3426 feat: improve queue ui (#1222)

## What's Changed
* fix: dotenv issue & `workingDir` field by @yottahmd in https://github.com/dagu-org/dagu/pull/1212
* [#1196] feat: Return error when `maxActiveRun=1` and a DAG-run for the same DAG is currently running by @yottahmd in https://github.com/dagu-org/dagu/pull/1213
* [#1196] feat: Enforce DAG-level `maxActiveRuns` configuration in API and CLI when starting a DAG-run by @yottahmd in https://github.com/dagu-org/dagu/pull/1214
* feat: rename `queue.maxActiveRuns` to `queue.maxConcurrency` by @yottahmd in https://github.com/dagu-org/dagu/pull/1215
* feat: improve check logic for `maxActiveRuns` by @yottahmd in https://github.com/dagu-org/dagu/pull/1216
* feat: Queue dashboard UI by @yottahmd in https://github.com/dagu-org/dagu/pull/1217
* feat(ui): Input DAG name modal by @yottahmd in https://github.com/dagu-org/dagu/pull/1218
* [#1209] fix: parallel issue by @yottahmd in https://github.com/dagu-org/dagu/pull/1219
* feat: apply feedbacks on queue UI by @yottahmd in https://github.com/dagu-org/dagu/pull/1221
* feat: improve queue ui by @yottahmd in https://github.com/dagu-org/dagu/pull/1222


**Full Changelog**: https://github.com/dagu-org/dagu/compare/v1.21.0...v1.22.0
